2. é¸æ“‡ Elements/å…ƒç´  æ¨™ç±¤
3. æ‰¾åˆ° `.toaster` æˆ– `[data-sonner-toaster]` å…ƒç´ 
4. æª¢æŸ¥ Computed æ¨£å¼ï¼š
   - âœ… `position: fixed`
   - âœ… `z-index: 9999`
   - âœ… `pointer-events: none`

